    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Bratislava Town Council (Augsburg, 29 May 1548) </head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">Gergely Bornemisza will recount quite a few things to
                            them, they should welcome him and do what he asks them in his name.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Prudentes et Circumspecti Domini et Amici Honorandissimi, salutem et
                    nostri commendationem!</p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Referet vel nuntiabit nonnulla Dominationibus Vestris nomine nostro
                    egregius dominus <persName>Gregorius Bornemyza</persName><note type="critic"
                        xml:id="note.1">Gergely Bornemisza. According this letter, he sent Gergely
                        Bornemisza, but that is likely to have been a mistake, and he was talking
                        about Pál Bornemisza, see Ep. 685.<ref>olahus.tei.15480602_1</ref></note>
                    aulicus regius. Rogamus igitur Dominationes Vestras, velint amicitiae nostrae
                    intuitu ea perficere, ad quae praefatus Bornemyza easdem nomine nostro rogaverit
                    et hortabitur, ut gratias eisdem coram habere et referre possimus.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Dominationes Vestrae bene valeant.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4">Ex <placeName>Augusta Vindelicorum</placeName> 29. Maii 1548.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.5">
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Nicolaus Olahus episcopus Zagrabiensis
                            cancellarius regiae maiestatis etc. manu propria</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.6">Prudentibus et circumspectis domino magistro civium iudici et
                    iuratis civibus civitatis Posoniensis dominis et amicis nobis
                    honorandissimis.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
